Package: plantFigR
Type: Package
Title: Gene Regulatory Network Inference for Plant Single-Cell Multi-omics Data
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: person("Kabilan", "S", email = "kabilan151414@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Contains functions to infer gene regulatory networks from
    unpaired or paired single-cell RNA-seq and ATAC-seq data for plant species.
    This package adapts the FigR framework to work with custom BSgenome,
    EnsDb, and plant‑specific TF motif libraries.
